## How will you know if there is a Disaster in progress?

No doubt you may have some alarms firing depending on how you have your alerting set up.

If there is a wider issues with the platform we will notifiy all users via #cloud-platform-update channel in line with our [operational processes](https://user-guide.cloud-platform.service.justice.gov.uk/documentation/reference/operational-processes.html#cloud-platform-update-slack-channel). You should check back here for periodic updates.

If we identify a specifiuc issue relating to a single service we will contact teams via the `slack-channel` annotation detailed in your namespace.

